{"tid":1861960,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新加坡首次有本土人傳人個案,　當局指未有社區廣泛傳播","createTime":"2020-02-04T11:24:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T12:00:02.000Z","uid":134071,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6bcf676ca64a161c73f8ff25ee5d187dae5236e4","tid":1861960,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T11:24:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1506625-20200204.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1506625-20200204.htm&d=pyoTqnfnoeQhQMJnYGDXlH4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=ae05329a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1506625-20200204.htm&h=74f769bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1506625-20200204.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n新加坡首次有本土人傳人個案 當局指未有社區廣泛傳播<br />\n2020-02-04 HKT 19:10<br />\n<br />\n新加坡首次出現本土人傳人的新型冠狀病毒肺炎確診病例。<br />\n<br />\n衛生部門表示，當地今日新增6宗個案，累計有24宗。新增患者當中，有4人是經本地傳播，包括兩名主要接待中國遊客的健康產品店店員、一名印傭及一名女導遊。另外，兩名由武漢返國的新加坡人亦出現感染徵狀。<br />\n<br />\n衛生部門的聲明指出，暫時未有證據表明，新型肺炎在新加坡社區持續廣泛傳播。"},{"pid":"43c308d5eff2e15f7e2492dc518f1335b71744b0","tid":1861960,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T11:24:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e8fb2b1bb3c6c5a1f2cdd8929aec9bcedf457f5","tid":1861960,"uid":89063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T11:25:20.000Z","msg":"奶共奶出禍"},{"pid":"3245b080da1e05d920d61df67032e9dd36ab8c77","tid":1861960,"uid":194326,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T11:25:39.000Z","msg":"今鋪真係大撚鑊<br />\n公司主要serve 中國tourists <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6ef1863283f47425abffb94fda005d25cc56eb1","tid":1861960,"uid":152476,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T11:26:47.000Z","msg":"確診仲多過香港<img src=\"/